column2: Let's Play DEADBOLT 01 - It's The Mr. Skullhead Game
column7:
Starring him, Mr. Skullhead.

DEADBOLT is a game about being dead and then meeting people who are dead and then killing them until they are somehow more dead. DEADBOLT looks a bit like Gunpoint and plays a bit like Hotline Miami. DEADBOLT is always spelled with all caps and I don't know why.
Get it on Steam at http://store.steampowered.com/app/394970/

It was that or "Ash Wednesday".

column2: Let's Play DEADBOLT 07 - Dumb Man's Switch
column7:
